===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{m|enm|gripen}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{m|ang|grīpan}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{m|gem-pro|*grīpaną}}, from {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} {{m|ine-pro|*gʰreyb-||to grab, grasp}}. Cognate with West Frisian {{m|fy|gripe}}, Low German {{m|nds|griepen}}, Dutch {{m|nl|grijpen}}, German {{m|de|greifen}}, Danish {{m|da|gribe}}, Swedish {{m|sv|gripa}}. See also {{l|en|grip}}, {{l|en|grope}}.

